  "label": "Saltglass Courtyard House",
  "description": "Saltglass Courtyard House constitutes a low basalt residence built on a salt-cemented plinth in keeping with Brineshade Terminator City’s fused platforms. Its plan turns inward around a narrow courtyard roofed by ribbed panes of saltglass that diffuse Saltharrow’s hard white glare into a constant, pale illumination. Shuttered arcades and layered light baffles line the exterior openings, preserving optical clarity while sealing against mineral haze bands. Interior walls bear mineral-wash finishes and load-buttresses engineered to resist the city’s measurable tidal stresses.",
